reviewText: I bought this video because I thought it would be a neauvo, tacky and fun addition to my Shakespeare collection. It was awful. It is simply a collection of strippers doing what they do best - stripping. If your  looking for Shakespeare, sure they spout of four or five lines here and  there but the content is minimul. Basically, it was awful and there was no  entertainment value. Try a porn website for a better collection of  strippers. That's all it is - without the overpriced drinks, smokey  atmosphere and drunken crowd.  The only advantage - you don't need a wallet  filled with dollar bills.
